 1991-23741991-11-280,  ANDRE,  ,  , 
PrecisAuthority for CINA HOLDINGS B.V., a wholly-owned subsidiary of the Canada Post Corporation, to sell some of its shares in itself to other postal administrations, or to otherwise dispose of them in their favour, provided that the Canada Post Corporation, either directly or indirectly, continues to hold five per cent (5%) or more of the issued shares of GD Net B.V.
